      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is just so quiet now. i wake up and for a split second i forget... and then i remember he's not coming back. it feels like i'm just walking through a ghost story. what's even the point of getting up and doing everything if he's not here to see it? everything feels so heavy and pointless.",
