    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>careful about the \"bridge\" thing. it's not that I want to erase him... it's just that the life I have left feels like a hollow shell. like i'm just performing these little tasks for a person who doesn't exist anymore. it feels less like living and more like just... waiting for the clock to run out. everything is just so empty.",
