      "content": "surviving feels so exhausting though. like i'm just dragging this weight around every single day and for what? to sit in this quiet house and wait for more days of nothing? it's hard to believe the light is ever coming back when it feels like the world just stopped when he died. it honestly feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just... stop fighting it.",
